title: SwiftTEA: Initial Red (Taylor's Version) Reaction... WE ARE ALL TOO UNWELL!
description:
Who else stayed up all night to binge this beautiful album? Who listened to it for the first time in it's entirety? WHAT ARE YOUR THOUGHTS ON THE 10 MIN VERSION? So much to discuss! Here's our initial reaction to the re-release, and what we have planned for next week.
... and we haven't even gotten to the short film yet! Is anyone else losing it yet?
What did we miss? What's your fav so far? What are you excited for us to get to? Let us know!
